<!-- Text -->
<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">
        <p>Skipping Stones is an experimental sound and poetry toy. Players throw stones accross a lake and create musical tones with each skip of the stone. It's an escape into an interactive music and poetry world isolated from the usual distractions.</p>
        <p>Follow the development on <a href="http://www.pressr1.com">Saleem's blog</a>. Sound composition by <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Mars-Module/316021549028?fref=ts">Mars Module.</a></p>
    </div>
</div>

